Validate that the move is within the range of the board aka 1-7
Validate that the move isn't in a column that that's full
Validate that the player will always pick a move that wins
Validate that the player will always block a winning move, assuming there's not a winning move
Validate the player can parse the board state
Validate the player can determine winning states
Validate the player can distinguish pieces
Validate that the player knows what a legal board looks like
  eg. no floating pieces
